                     <interp inst="t18270405-164-person973" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard the cry of Stop thief! I followed, and met Faulkner bringing the prisoner back - he begged for forgiveness in the shop.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. He stated at the office that the tray was outside his house.</p>
               <p>PROSECUTOR. Yes, it was tied to the iron rail.</p>
